Introduction

:use BODY
Turn your computer off and put it in the closet.
 100 years from now someone finds it and powers it up.

:use SIZE_2
:use FG_MAGENTA
Does it boot?
:use FG_BODY
 Probably.

:use FG_MAGENTA
Do your applications still run?
:use FG_BODY
 Maybe..

:use FG_MAGENTA
Can you install new software on it?
:use FG_BODY
 Not a chance.
