:use HEADER
Limitations

:translate 0 -0.05
:use BODY
Software is stable when its dependencies are stable.

:use BULLET1
What dependencies?

:use BULLET2
Dynamically linked (shared) libraries

:use BULLET2
Operating system interface, (like system calls)

:use BULLET2
Library/OS ABI
